  "detailed_description": "Peppered is a real-time strategy game about snowball fights!<br><br>You command a group of friends in snowball fights against kids around the neighborhood.<br>Make them scoop up snow, let them throw snowball at opponents and build snow walls to defend yourself.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> ~30min playtime<br></li><li> 4 challengers</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213600/extras/216d8c8961b0a26f270609b1f991845c.poster.avif?t=1639495206\" width=560 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213600/extras/216d8c8961b0a26f270609b1f991845c.webm?t=1639495206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213600/extras/216d8c8961b0a26f270609b1f991845c.mp4?t=1639495206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each time a kid gets hit they will become colder and colder. If they become too cold they'll run home crying.<br>However, each side has a campfire where they can warm-up and \"recover\".<br>Extinguishing the opponent's campfire first can pay-off later!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213600/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1639495206\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
